Package: rnassqs_helper
Title: Helper Tools for Simplified Access to USDA NASS Quick Stats
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "First",
        family = "Last",
        email = "you@company.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides a streamlined interface for downloading, cleaning, 
    and managing data from the USDA NASS Quick Stats API. This package 
    wraps common query patterns, handles pagination, and simplifies 
    authentication and data retrieval workflows for analysts and 
    researchers working with agricultural datasets.
